      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i've had bad indigestion before and its felt like this. i'm pretty sure it's just the grease from the pizza. i dont really want to go to the er if i can avoid it, it's so expensive and the wait is always hours. if i take a couple of extra antacids and maybe some aspirin, do u think that'll help clear it up pretty quick so i can just sleep it off?",
