      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but honestly i feel way too nauseous to even get in the car right now. plus the arm thing is more like a dull ache, not like the sharp pain people talk about in movies. if i just take 4 tums and a 325mg aspirin right now, is there any reason that would be dangerous? i just want to know if that's a safe way to handle this at home since i'm really not feeling up to a hospital trip.",
